---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services — Projexions"
  description="Practical bookkeeping solutions for businesses that need to move forward. Monthly bookkeeping, cleanup, and diagnostic tools."
  currentPath="/services"
>
  <div class="page-container">
    <h1 class="serif-heading text-4xl font-semibold mb-4 text-center">How Projexions Helps</h1>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 text-center max-w-prose mx-auto">
      Practical bookkeeping solutions for businesses that need to move forward.
    </p>

    <div class="services-card">
      <div class="prose-content">

        <!-- Monthly Bookkeeping -->
        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Monthly Bookkeeping</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle text-center">For established businesses seeking a high-touch, long-term partner.</p>

        <ul class="resource-list text-lg mb-6">
          <li><strong>Limited Capacity:</strong> Projexions maintains a small client roster to ensure every account gets technical oversight.</li>
          <li><strong>Ongoing Maintenance:</strong> Reliable monthly reconciliations and categorization to keep your records stable year-round.</li>
          <li><strong>Selective Partnerships:</strong> We focus on quality over volume, maintaining a firm-level commitment to your data integrity.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="section-link text-center">
          <a href="/bookkeeping-west-hollywood">View details →</a>
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <!-- Bookkeeping Cleanup -->
        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Bookkeeping Cleanup</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle text-center">For businesses that have fallen behind and need to get tax-ready.</p>

        <ul class="resource-list text-lg mb-6">
          <li><strong>Catch-Up & Reconciliation:</strong> Reconciling months or years of neglected bank and credit card activity.</li>
          <li><strong>Platform Stabilization:</strong> Fixing messy data flows from Stripe, Shopify, and e-commerce platforms.</li>
          <li><strong>CPA Readiness:</strong> Delivering organized, usable records so your tax professional can file without delays.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="section-link text-center">
          <a href="/bookkeeping-cleanup">Explore the process →</a>
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <!-- Diagnostic Tools -->
        <h2 class="section-title text-center">The Diagnostic Tools</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle text-center">Not sure how much help you need? Use these tools to find out.</p>

        <div class="option-block">
          <h3 class="option-title text-center">Free Bookkeeping Estimator</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Get an instant, realistic projection of the hours and effort your cleanup will take.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-2"><strong>How it works:</strong> A 2-minute quiz based on your bank activity and tech stack.</p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4"><strong>Result:</strong> An immediate estimate of time and cost.</p>
          <div class="section-cta">
            <a href="/estimator" class="btn-primary">Take the Quiz</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="option-block">
          <h3 class="option-title text-center">Tax Readiness Evaluation</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            A structured, one-time professional review of your current records.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4"><strong>Includes:</strong> A 60-minute call and a written Tax Readiness Map (PDF).</p>
          <p class="section-link text-center">
            <a href="/tax-season-bookkeeping-readiness">View evaluation details →</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <!-- Bookkeeper Hiring Help -->
        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Bookkeeper Hiring Help</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle text-center">For businesses about to hire who want a technical second opinion.</p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          <strong>The Result:</strong> A written risk summary identifying technical red flags and competency signals before you sign a contract.
        </p>

        <p class="section-link text-center">
          <a href="/hiring-help">Review the process →</a>
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <!-- FAQ -->
        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How long does a cleanup take?</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            It depends on complexity. Some take a few days; others take longer. We once reconciled a full year in 12 hours.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How much will this cost?</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We scope by project complexity rather than fixed packages. Use the <a href="/estimator">Estimator</a> for an instant projection.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Why a developer-led approach?</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            It allows us to fix broken data flows (like Stripe or Shopify) more precisely than manual data entry.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Do you provide tax filing?</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            No. Projexions provides organized data so your CPA can file accurately and easily.
          </p>
        </div>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <!-- Important Boundaries -->
        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Important Boundaries</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Projexions provides organizational review and bookkeeping stabilization only. No accounting, tax, legal, or financial advice is provided.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .services-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--ui-gray);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .section-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ui-gray);
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }

  .section-cta {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-link {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .section-link a {
    color: var(--brand-green);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .section-link a:hover {
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .dual-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    color: var(--text-gray);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .option-block {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--bg-section-alt);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .option-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--brand-green);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
